The spoon.

323
00:19:38,850 --> 00:19:39,610
The tweezers.

324
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:40,740
The scissors.

325
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:42,020
The block.

326
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:43,500
The axe.

327
00:19:43,850 --> 00:19:44,660
The needle.

328
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:45,770
And the scraper.

