00:20:46,660 --> 00:20:47,460
Good one!

348
00:20:47,850 --> 00:20:50,220
Then, who's next?

349
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:51,740
Old Madam,

350
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:55,700
why don't we
let Third Young Mistress go next?

351
00:20:56,130 --> 00:20:58,090
She can show us how graceful

352
00:20:58,090 --> 00:21:00,460
a gentlewoman from Yangzhou eats crabs,

353
00:21:01,020 --> 00:21:03,220
while composing a masterpiece.

