00:21:12,850 --> 00:21:14,660
Wisdom in hold, elegance in mold.

359
00:21:14,810 --> 00:21:17,180
Third Young Mistress
is surely the best candidate.

360
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:21,700
Well...

361
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:28,180
[The little axe and hammers]

362
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:30,610
