366
00:21:36,130 --> 00:21:36,610
Go ahead.

367
00:21:41,770 --> 00:21:43,530
Cut off the tail and rip off the legs,

368
00:21:52,130 --> 00:21:54,700
Hit the back and hammer the chest.

369
00:22:00,770 --> 00:22:03,220
Lift up the shell and pierce the heart

370
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:13,180
Taste the meat with tongue of sword.

371
00:22:25,850 --> 00:22:26,770
Good.

