There's no need to be too girlish.

386
00:23:15,130 --> 00:23:16,050
That's why

387
00:23:16,130 --> 00:23:17,460
he had Her Ladyship

388
00:23:17,610 --> 00:23:19,370
read a lot of frontier fortress poems.

389
00:23:19,660 --> 00:23:22,260
So her style is naturally bold and heroic.

390
00:23:25,130 --> 00:23:26,020
That's right, Grandmother.

391
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:27,700
I love frontier fortress poems.

392
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,660
Who would have thought Third Young Mistress

393
00:23:29,810 --> 00:23:31,420
