394
00:23:32,220 --> 00:23:33,020
Of course.

395
00:23:33,370 --> 00:23:35,290
Females are as excellent
as their male peers.

396
00:23:38,290 --> 00:23:39,050
Old Madam,

397
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:42,740
the chrysanthemums are ready outside.

398
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:45,050
Why don't we go out

399
00:23:45,260 --> 00:23:46,700
to appreciate them and draw pictures?

400
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:48,850
Good idea.

401
00:23:49,290 --> 00:23:50,090
Let's go.

402
00:23:50,660 --> 00:23:53,980
Let's see our chrysanthemums at the door.

403
00:23:54,290 --> 00:23:55,090
Bingyan,

404
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:56,570
Old Madam used to be

405
00:23:56,570 --> 00:23:58,500
a famous woman painter.

406
00:23:59,020 --> 00:24:00,940
You're also a famous gentlewoman
from Yangzhou.

407
00:24:01,290 --> 00:24:02,980
I trust that you must be good at

408
00:24:02,980 --> 00:24:05,370
all the fancies of men of letters.

409
00:24:06,050 --> 00:24:06,850
So today,

410
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:08,850
do show us your excellent skills.

411
00:24:11,570 --> 00:24:13,980
Why don't you draw
that White Phoenix Pearl?

412
00:24:20,850 --> 00:24:21,420
Okay.

413
00:24:22,330 --> 00:24:24,330
Okay, then let's all get started.

414
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:24,940
Okay.

415
00:24:33,220 --> 00:24:34,900
It's so hard to be a gentlewoman.

416
00:24:35,290 --> 00:24:36,020
Your Ladyship,

417
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:37,770
you must hang on.

418
00:24:37,770 --> 00:24:39,420
I can hang on when I'm doing chin-ups.

419
00:24:40,530 --> 00:24:41,770
But the literary stuff...

420
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,260
I'll do my best.

421
00:25:07,740 --> 00:25:09,020
Oh, chrysanthemum.

422
00:25:10,130 --> 00:25:11,530
You're the White Phoenix Pearl,

423
00:25:12,530 --> 00:25:14,900
and I am the Tanned Black Bug.

424
00:25:16,290 --> 00:25:18,130
I should've studied harder

425
00:25:18,130 --> 00:25:19,290
when dad sent me to school.

426
00:26:24,610 --> 00:26:25,370
Old Madam,

427
00:26:25,770 --> 00:26:28,220
the Red Lips you drew looks so vivid.

428
00:26:28,770 --> 00:26:31,090
What a graceful painting.

429
00:26:33,330 --> 00:26:35,020
Third Young Mistress has also finished.

430
00:26:36,660 --> 00:26:39,460
Let's all take a look at Bingyan's work.

431
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:44,770
Grandmother,

432
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:46,500
actually I'm not good at drawing.

433
00:26:46,770 --> 00:26:48,090
It's okay.

434
00:26:48,330 --> 00:26:50,460
These are just for fun.

435
00:26:50,980 --> 00:26:52,610
Let mother have the first look.

436
00:27:04,570 --> 00:27:05,420
Bingyan,

437
00:27:05,850 --> 00:27:07,460
how did you draw

438
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:09,050
with this seal-like style?

439
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:10,460
Watch this now.

440
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:17,180
This style is so unique

441
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,900
and so special.

442
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:21,050
It's a whole new experience.

443
00:27:21,330 --> 00:27:23,180
Great!

444
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:25,500
Let me have a closer look.

445
00:27:27,290 --> 00:27:27,900
This...

