00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:29,530
Grandmother,

447
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:31,770
I'm a little hungry.

448
00:27:34,020 --> 00:27:36,770
We spent too much time
on poems and drawing

449
00:27:37,290 --> 00:27:38,610
and forgot to let her eat.

450
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:39,290
Okay.

451
00:27:39,530 --> 00:27:40,570
What do you like to have?

452
00:27:40,570 --> 00:27:41,700
I'll take you.

