00:27:42,220 --> 00:27:44,330
I'd like to have sweet-and-sour ribs

454
00:27:45,370 --> 00:27:46,260
and braised pork.

455
00:27:46,460 --> 00:27:47,130
No problem.

456
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:50,090
Sweet-and-sour ribs and braised pork.

457
00:27:50,530 --> 00:27:51,940
Tell the kitchen to serve these.

458
00:27:52,290 --> 00:27:53,260
Sheng'er, come on.

459
00:27:54,260 --> 00:27:55,180
Careful, Grandmother.

460
00:27:55,420 --> 00:27:56,290
Okay.

