00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:35,020
[This is your daughter
hoping you well.]

463
00:28:36,260 --> 00:28:37,810
[You would never have imagined]

464
00:28:38,940 --> 00:28:41,220
[I was married wrongly
to General Yuan's mansion in Jingzhou.]

