00:28:42,460 --> 00:28:44,290
[Now I'm like living in prison.]

466
00:28:46,850 --> 00:28:49,770
[Sincerely yours,
Bingyan]

467
00:28:56,780 --> 00:29:03,020
[Sincerely yours]

468
00:29:15,530 --> 00:29:17,220
Even if I didn't get
on the wrong bridal sedan,

469
00:29:18,330 --> 00:29:19,850
being married to the Qi Residence
in Linzhou

470
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:23,370
to counteract bad luck for a dying man

471
00:29:24,740 --> 00:29:26,460
is not much better than this.

472
00:29:33,770 --> 00:29:35,810
I wonder what's going on with sister Yuhu.

473
00:29:36,610 --> 00:29:37,850
Could she be like me?

474
00:29:39,900 --> 00:29:40,810
Did she go to Linzhou

475
00:29:42,770 --> 00:29:43,940
and end up in a fire pit?

476
00:29:49,940 --> 00:29:50,940
Sister Yuhu,

477
00:29:53,290 --> 00:29:54,500
how are you now?

478
00:30:02,340 --> 00:30:06,420
[Dear Father and Mother, this is your daughter
hoping you well. You would never have imagined]

479
00:30:06,420 --> 00:30:09,420
[I was married wrongly
to General Yuan's mansion in Jingzhou.]

480
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:14,420
[Now I'm like living in prison.]
[Sincerely yours, Bingyan]

481
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:19,500
This is so boring.

482
00:30:21,810 --> 00:30:23,500
If I stay in here a bit longer,

483
00:30:24,020 --> 00:30:26,130
my kung fu will get rusty.

484
00:30:44,740 --> 00:30:45,460
Your Ladyship.

485
00:30:47,900 --> 00:30:48,940
Your Ladyship.

486
00:30:49,090 --> 00:30:49,810
Remember,

487
00:30:50,020 --> 00:30:52,260
you're now Miss Du,

488
00:30:52,260 --> 00:30:53,810
